We are the fastest growing Network marketing company in India. Join the Nebula Family! Nebula™ User Privacy Policy
Being a resolute Network Marketing Company the top priority of Nebula ™ will always be the relationship with its members/associates. We collect information that you would provide directly to us based on the scope of our Nebula™ app. Nebula™, as data controller, when activating and using the Nebula™ Services, how Nebula™ receives, collects and uses this data and how you may opt-out at any time, altogether preventing use of the data shared via the Services. Installation and Use After you install and use the Nebula™ App, Nebula™ will collect, process and retain personal information from you and any devices you may use connected with our application. This information may include the following: Storage, geo-location, telephone access, Your IP address, device manufacturer and type, Data operator, IMEI, connection information, screen resolution, camera, usage statistics and device log. This will help us serve you better. Map & Location Information: Nebula™ app would have the access of Google Maps and Location services to enable you to locate our offices from the app itself and we will have a log of your location so that we can provide you the locations of your marketing network and downline members. Similarly members who have you in their marketing network will be able to track your location. Your location will not be public but will be accessible to your direct upline members only. Contacts Information: If you permit the Nebula™ app to access the address book on your device, we may access and store names and contact information from your address book to enable marketing interactions of the concerned contacts based on their history. We will send marketing SMS, emails and/or call your contacts from your phone book. Your contact book is completely private with us and is only meant for marketing and promotional purposes. Device Information: We may collect information about your mobile device, including, for example, the hardware model, operating system and version, software version, IMEI, unique device identifier, advertising identifiers, serial number, device motion information, device IP address and mobile network information. This info will help us understand the device specific issues and help us resolve errors with more precision. Your device information will remain confidential and private with us. Nebula™may use Push Notification Services to notify you about up-dates and important information. In such cases, your phone number may be part of the notification. This message is sent to the push notification service provider, for delivery to your device. You may, however, at any time-opt out or disable push notifications in the Nebula™app. Nebula™app will upload your personal details and your device information on a secure server. This information stored on our server is never circulated or shared with any third party applications or entities. Please note that Nebula™ or Nebula Companies do not responsibility if a user copies, uploads downline data on a third party app or any other server. Please be very cautious before sharing your data with any third party app claiming to be associated with us. Nebula™ app is not responsible for any loss of user data. Terms and Conditions For Star Platinum and Above NV will be calculated from 2nd and 3rd legs, whereas for any rank below Star Platinum, maximum 10000 NV will be considered from Power leg, balance has to be covered in 2nd and 3rd leg. NV generated from new sales can contribute for only 3 qualifications for both the promotions. NV will be calculated on Placement tree. The rank at the end of the promotion period shall be considered for qualification. This promotion will only be valid on new bookings made between 6th Aug 2018 to 28th Oct 2018. NV generated from Token and Spot Down Payment shall be considered for these promotions. If the company foresees any cancellation or dispute in any new sale, then that particular sale shall not be counted. Management reserves the right to discontinue the promotion at any point of time. Management reserves the right to disqualify any IBO on the basis of unethical practices. For International trip qualifiers: IBO must have a valid Passport with minimum 6 Months validity or as per government rules at the time of travel. The IBO must be fit enough for air travel. Visa is not included in this promotion. It is the sole responsibility of the IBO to get the visa however management may help facilitate the visa process. This promotion is non-transferable and cannot be encashed. A sale will be considered complete only when the token amount is cleared with PDCs for EMIs/ECS application and complete loan documents have been received. These promotions will not be exchanged for any other promotion. On demand, at any time during the promotion all the qualifiers must present the passport and other required documents for Air tickets and hotel bookings. Its mandatory for all the qualifiers to attend the leadership development training program (all sessions). At any point during the promotions Nebula reserves the right to discontinue the trip of any qualifier. Nebula shall only be sponsoring for fixed inclusions- rest all the other expenses are to be borne by the qualifier. Nebula reserves the right to make any changes in the promotions.
Dwarka Thailand (Bangkok-Pattaya)
Eligibility Criteria IBO must be ranked Star Platinum and above and have new sales with 45000 NV in his down-line before the end of the promotion. The Star Platinum has direct sales of 12 apartments of Nebula’s Aavaas Changodar (Ahmedabad) or Nebula’s Aavaas Miyapur (Hyderabad) or combination of both the project sales. The Star Platinum has direct sales of 5 villas in Hawthorn Suites in Dwarka. The Star Platinum has Direct Sales/Sponsored 45 Nebula’s Thailand Holiday packages.
IBO ranked below Star Platinum with new sales of 20000 NV in his down-line before the end of the promotion is qualified for this Promo. The IBO has direct sales of 7 apartments of Nebula’s Aavaas Changodar (Ahmedabad) or Nebula’s Aavaas Miyapur (Hyderabad) or combination of both the project sales. The IBO has direct sales of 3 villas in Hawthorn Suites in Dwarka. The IBO has Direct Sales/Sponsored 25 Nebula’s Thailand Holiday packages.
